mmc: dw_mmc: init desc in dw_mci_idmac_init

Set 0 to des1 in 32bit case.
Otherwise the random value of des1 will be used in
dw_mci_translate_sglist: IDMAC_SET_BUFFER1_SIZE(desc, length)

